00:56:14.110 --> 00:56:14.904
JAKE TAPPER: Yeah.

00:56:14.904 --> 00:56:16.570
AUDIENCE: And it just
seems like a waste

00:56:16.570 --> 00:56:18.580
of that segment of the show.

00:56:18.580 --> 00:56:19.187
So--

00:56:19.187 --> 00:56:20.270
JAKE TAPPER: So why do it?

00:56:20.270 --> 00:56:21.353
AUDIENCE: Why have her on?

00:56:21.353 --> 00:56:23.363
JAKE TAPPER: Why have her on?

00:56:23.363 --> 00:56:27.828
So you're not the first
person to ask me this week.

00:56:27.828 --> 00:56:30.239
[LAUGHTER]

00:56:30.239 --> 00:56:32.530
I did at an event at the 92nd
Street Y Wednesday night,

00:56:32.530 --> 00:56:34.488
and Stephen Colbert asked
me the same question.

00:56:34.488 --> 00:56:36.470
So you're in good company.

